Package: qshapr
Type: Package
Title: Fast Calculation of Feature Contributions in Boosting Trees
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-02-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("Steven", "He", role = "aut", email = "hess1@uci.edu"),
    person("Zhongli", "Jiang", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "zhongli.jiang.stats@gmail.com"),
    person("Dabao", "Zhang", role = "aut", email = "zdb969@hs.uci.edu"),
    person("Min", "Zhang", role = "aut")
)
Description: Computes feature-specific R-squared values using Shapley decomposition 
    of the total R-squared for Boosting Trees in polynomial time. Supports XGBoost 
    and LightGBM models with parallel processing capabilities. Based on the method 
    described in Jiang, Zhang, and Zhang (2025) "Fast Calculation of Feature 
    Contributions in Boosting Trees".
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/catstats/Q-SHAP_R
